a good amount of throttle to get out. So upon giving it gas the first time 
the engine stalled. I thought it stalled because I didn't give it enough 
gas. So I started the bus up again, revved the engine a little higher and 
again it dies only this time when I go to restart it there is no electrical 
juice. Absolutely nothing. I go to the back, look into the engine 
