to pinpoint anything. I felt the ground wire from the battery and it felt 
unusually warm. Does anyone have any Ideas as to what the problem might be? 
The vehicle is a 75 and it's fuel injected. I replaced the main computer 
about a year ago. Any help would be most appreciated.

